<subSubSection pageId="9" pageNumber="417" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,459,644,704]" box="[151,302,679,704]" pageId="9" pageNumber="417">
(
<figureCitation box="[159,294,679,704]" captionStart="FIGURES 43–53" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1907,1930]" captionTargetBox="[229,1370,202,1866]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[216,1374,193,1896]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 43–53. Kalasha aequalis sp. n., Holotype ♂: 43. Habitus, dorsal view; 44. Habitus, lateral view; 45. Head and thorax, dorsal view; 46. Face; 47. Genital capsule, ventral view; 48. Subgenital plate, ventral view; 49. Aedeagus, connective and style, lateral view; 50. Aedeagus, lateral view; 51. Pygofer ventral process, ventral view; 52. Aedeagus, connective and style, dorsal view; 53. Connective and style Apophysis, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2618974/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="417">Figs. 43–53</figureCitation>
)
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1437,751,1640]" box="[151,633,751,776]" pageId="9" pageNumber="417">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,237,751,776]" pageId="9" pageNumber="417">Length</emphasis>
(including forewing): 
<specimenCount box="[491,514,752,775]" pageId="9" pageNumber="417" type="male">♂</specimenCount>
, 10.0 mm.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1437,751,1640]" pageId="9" pageNumber="417">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,462,788,813]" pageId="9" pageNumber="417">External morphology.</emphasis>
Body dark brown. Crown (
<figureCitation box="[780,863,788,813]" captionStart="FIGURES 43–53" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1907,1930]" captionTargetBox="[229,1370,202,1866]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[216,1374,193,1896]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 43–53. Kalasha aequalis sp. n., Holotype ♂: 43. Habitus, dorsal view; 44. Habitus, lateral view; 45. Head and thorax, dorsal view; 46. Face; 47. Genital capsule, ventral view; 48. Subgenital plate, ventral view; 49. Aedeagus, connective and style, lateral view; 50. Aedeagus, lateral view; 51. Pygofer ventral process, ventral view; 52. Aedeagus, connective and style, dorsal view; 53. Connective and style Apophysis, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2618974/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="417">Fig. 45</figureCitation>
) slightly shorter than wide. Face (
<figureCitation box="[1257,1341,788,813]" captionStart="FIGURES 43–53" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1907,1930]" captionTargetBox="[229,1370,202,1866]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[216,1374,193,1896]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 43–53. Kalasha aequalis sp. n., Holotype ♂: 43. Habitus, dorsal view; 44. Habitus, lateral view; 45. Head and thorax, dorsal view; 46. Face; 47. Genital capsule, ventral view; 48. Subgenital plate, ventral view; 49. Aedeagus, connective and style, lateral view; 50. Aedeagus, lateral view; 51. Pygofer ventral process, ventral view; 52. Aedeagus, connective and style, dorsal view; 53. Connective and style Apophysis, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2618974/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="417">Fig. 46</figureCitation>
) shorter than width including eyes, lateral margins of gena slightly concave and apex of gena truncate. Pronotum (
<figureCitation captionStart="FIGURES 43–53" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1907,1930]" captionTargetBox="[229,1370,202,1866]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[216,1374,193,1896]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 43–53. Kalasha aequalis sp. n., Holotype ♂: 43. Habitus, dorsal view; 44. Habitus, lateral view; 45. Head and thorax, dorsal view; 46. Face; 47. Genital capsule, ventral view; 48. Subgenital plate, ventral view; 49. Aedeagus, connective and style, lateral view; 50. Aedeagus, lateral view; 51. Pygofer ventral process, ventral view; 52. Aedeagus, connective and style, dorsal view; 53. Connective and style Apophysis, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2618974/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="417">Figs. 44, 45</figureCitation>
) with posterior margin slightly wider than anterior margin, maximum length shorter than width of anterior margin, posterior margin moderately concave. Exposed part of mesonotum and scutellum (
<figureCitation box="[1195,1334,895,920]" captionStart="FIGURES 43–53" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1907,1930]" captionTargetBox="[229,1370,202,1866]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[216,1374,193,1896]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 43–53. Kalasha aequalis sp. n., Holotype ♂: 43. Habitus, dorsal view; 44. Habitus, lateral view; 45. Head and thorax, dorsal view; 46. Face; 47. Genital capsule, ventral view; 48. Subgenital plate, ventral view; 49. Aedeagus, connective and style, lateral view; 50. Aedeagus, lateral view; 51. Pygofer ventral process, ventral view; 52. Aedeagus, connective and style, dorsal view; 53. Connective and style Apophysis, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2618974/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="417">Figs. 44, 45</figureCitation>
) slightly shorter than wide, nearly flat with tubercle poorly developed.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1437,751,1640]" pageId="9" pageNumber="417">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,378,967,992]" pageId="9" pageNumber="417">Male genitalia.</emphasis>
(
<figureCitation box="[396,532,967,992]" captionStart="FIGURES 43–53" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1907,1930]" captionTargetBox="[229,1370,202,1866]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[216,1374,193,1896]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 43–53. Kalasha aequalis sp. n., Holotype ♂: 43. Habitus, dorsal view; 44. Habitus, lateral view; 45. Head and thorax, dorsal view; 46. Face; 47. Genital capsule, ventral view; 48. Subgenital plate, ventral view; 49. Aedeagus, connective and style, lateral view; 50. Aedeagus, lateral view; 51. Pygofer ventral process, ventral view; 52. Aedeagus, connective and style, dorsal view; 53. Connective and style Apophysis, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2618974/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="417">Figs. 47–52</figureCitation>
) Pygofer (
<figureCitation box="[656,739,967,992]" captionStart="FIGURES 43–53" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1907,1930]" captionTargetBox="[229,1370,202,1866]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[216,1374,193,1896]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 43–53. Kalasha aequalis sp. n., Holotype ♂: 43. Habitus, dorsal view; 44. Habitus, lateral view; 45. Head and thorax, dorsal view; 46. Face; 47. Genital capsule, ventral view; 48. Subgenital plate, ventral view; 49. Aedeagus, connective and style, lateral view; 50. Aedeagus, lateral view; 51. Pygofer ventral process, ventral view; 52. Aedeagus, connective and style, dorsal view; 53. Connective and style Apophysis, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2618974/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="417">Fig. 51</figureCitation>
) ventral process about 1/3 as long as pygofer side, extended mesad, branches long and slender, nearly parallel and comparatively far apart in ventral view, lateral branch above and approximately as long as central one in lateral view, more than ten microsetae present on base of branches. Subgenital plate (
<figureCitation box="[351,435,1076,1101]" captionStart="FIGURES 43–53" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1907,1930]" captionTargetBox="[229,1370,202,1866]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[216,1374,193,1896]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 43–53. Kalasha aequalis sp. n., Holotype ♂: 43. Habitus, dorsal view; 44. Habitus, lateral view; 45. Head and thorax, dorsal view; 46. Face; 47. Genital capsule, ventral view; 48. Subgenital plate, ventral view; 49. Aedeagus, connective and style, lateral view; 50. Aedeagus, lateral view; 51. Pygofer ventral process, ventral view; 52. Aedeagus, connective and style, dorsal view; 53. Connective and style Apophysis, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2618974/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="417">Fig. 48</figureCitation>
) somewhat shorter than 1/2 length of pygofer. Connective (
<figureCitation box="[1122,1349,1076,1101]" captionStart="FIGURES 43–53" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1907,1930]" captionTargetBox="[229,1370,202,1866]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[216,1374,193,1896]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 43–53. Kalasha aequalis sp. n., Holotype ♂: 43. Habitus, dorsal view; 44. Habitus, lateral view; 45. Head and thorax, dorsal view; 46. Face; 47. Genital capsule, ventral view; 48. Subgenital plate, ventral view; 49. Aedeagus, connective and style, lateral view; 50. Aedeagus, lateral view; 51. Pygofer ventral process, ventral view; 52. Aedeagus, connective and style, dorsal view; 53. Connective and style Apophysis, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2618974/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="417">Figs. 49, 50, 52, 53</figureCitation>
) length about 1.8x width, vertical process apex surpassing anterior margin in dorsal view. Style (
<figureCitation box="[1173,1356,1111,1136]" captionStart="FIGURES 43–53" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1907,1930]" captionTargetBox="[229,1370,202,1866]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[216,1374,193,1896]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 43–53. Kalasha aequalis sp. n., Holotype ♂: 43. Habitus, dorsal view; 44. Habitus, lateral view; 45. Head and thorax, dorsal view; 46. Face; 47. Genital capsule, ventral view; 48. Subgenital plate, ventral view; 49. Aedeagus, connective and style, lateral view; 50. Aedeagus, lateral view; 51. Pygofer ventral process, ventral view; 52. Aedeagus, connective and style, dorsal view; 53. Connective and style Apophysis, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2618974/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="417">Figs. 49, 52, 53</figureCitation>
) about 3.0x longer than connective, apophysis disc-like and curved laterad with 5–8 setae on ventral surface. Aedeagus (
<figureCitation box="[159,345,1183,1208]" captionStart="FIGURES 43–53" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1907,1930]" captionTargetBox="[229,1370,202,1866]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[216,1374,193,1896]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 43–53. Kalasha aequalis sp. n., Holotype ♂: 43. Habitus, dorsal view; 44. Habitus, lateral view; 45. Head and thorax, dorsal view; 46. Face; 47. Genital capsule, ventral view; 48. Subgenital plate, ventral view; 49. Aedeagus, connective and style, lateral view; 50. Aedeagus, lateral view; 51. Pygofer ventral process, ventral view; 52. Aedeagus, connective and style, dorsal view; 53. Connective and style Apophysis, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2618974/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="417">Figs. 49, 50, 52</figureCitation>
) broad and depressed in middle on dorsal surface, sides convex and with transverse rugae on dorsal surface throughout length, shaft moderately broad, gonopore at apex.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1437,751,1640]" box="[199,418,1255,1280]" pageId="9" pageNumber="417">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,293,1255,1280]" pageId="9" pageNumber="417">Female.</emphasis>
Unknown.
</paragraph>
